%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHindus%20Don't%20Indulge%20In%20Communalism%2C%20Only%20One%20Religion...%26quot%3B%3A%20Himanta%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20on%20Saturday%20claimed%20that%20members%20of%20the%20Bangladesh-origin%20minority%20community%20overwhelmingly%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20without%20considering%20the%20development%20work%20done%20for%20them%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20governments%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0He%20also%20alleged%20that%20it%20is%20the%20only%20community%20in%20Assam%20which%20indulges%20in%20communalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20felicitation%20programme%20of%20winning%20candidates%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20at%20the%20party's%20state%20headquarters%20here%2C%20he%20said%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20garnered%20nearly%2047%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20polled%2C%20while%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20bagged%2039%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-AGP-UPPL%20coalition%20won%2011%20out%20of%20the%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20Congress%20bagging%20the%20remaining%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20analyse%20the%2039%20per%20cent%20votes%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20not%20spread%20across%20the%20state.%20Fifty%20per%20cent%20of%20it%20is%20concentrated%20in%2021%20assembly%20segments%20which%20are%20minority%20dominated.%20In%20these%20minority-dominated%20segments%2C%20BJP%20got%203%20per%20cent%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20proves%20that%20Hindus%20do%20not%20indulge%20in%20communalism.%20If%20anyone%20indulges%20in%20communalism%20in%20Assam%2C%20it%20is%20only%20one%20community%2C%20one%20religion.%20No%20other%20religion%20does%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20asserted%2C%20without%20naming%20any%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20minority-dominated%20areas%20may%20have%20no%20roads%2C%20no%20electricity%2C%20but%20they%20have%20been%20voting%20overwhelmingly%20for%20Congress%20and%20did%20so%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20though%20BJP%20has%20been%20working%20for%20the%20Assamese%20people%20and%20tribals%2C%20these%20communities%20have%20not%20voted%20100%20per%20cent%20for%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExcept%20in%20Karimganj%2C%20if%20we%20consider%20the%20centres%20with%20majority%20Bangladesh-origin%20people%2C%2099%20per%20cent%20of%20votes%20have%20gone%20to%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(minority%20people)%20may%20be%20residing%20in%20houses%20given%20by%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi%2C%20availing%20electricity%20and%20sanitation%20facilities%20provided%20by%20Modi%2C%20but%20when%20they%20go%20to%20vote%2C%20they%20vote%20for%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20maintained%20that%20the%20Bangladesh-origin%20community%20will%20vote%20for%20Congress%20because%20they%20want%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%20the%20state%20in%20the%20next%2010%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20alleged%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20community%20attacked%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Lakhimpur%2C%20a%20village%20in%20Barpeta%20and%20tried%20to%20encroach%20land%20in%20Kokrajhar%20when%20the%20BJP%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Binactive%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC)%20was%20in%20place..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20BJP%20government%20will%20not%20be%20there%2C%20one%20can%20only%20imagine%20how%20many%20such%20attacks%20will%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20had%20won%2092%20out%20of%20126%20assembly%20segments%20in%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20which%20was%20the%20highest%20ever%20for%20any%20ruling%20alli