0makes%20were%20fired%20at%20Aman%20Joon%20inside%20the%20fast%20food%20outlet%2C%20the%20FIR%20says.%20The%20different%20bullets%20suggest%20that%20more%20than%20two%20weapons%20were%20used%20by%20the%20two%20shooters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20security%20camera%20footage%2C%20which%20was%20released%20earlier%2C%20Anu%20was%20seen%20sitting%20with%20Aman%20when%20the%20gunmen%20opened%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20has%20shown%20that%20Anu%20took%20a%20train%20from%20GTB%20Nagar%20Metro%20Station%20to%20reach%20Rajouri%20Garden%20and%20after%20the%20murder%2C%20she%20took%20the%20metro%20from%20Rajouri%20Garden%20to%20Shakurpur%20Metro%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8nk3lqc8_anu-_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman's%20body%20was%20found%20behind%20the%20billing%20counter%2C%20indicating%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20flee%20when%20the%20killers%20opened%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%20Bhau%2C%20suspected%20to%20be%20in%20Portugal%20now%2C%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Brevenge%20killing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%20Bhau%2C%20whose%20gang%20operates%20across%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana%2C%20is%20notorious%20for%20extortion%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%20Bhau%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20jailed%20gangster%20Neeraj%20Bawana%2C%20fled%20the%20country%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719125460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ffcgh0nmg_burger-king-murder_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fburger-king-shooting-burger-king-murder-aman-joon-anu-video-lady-don-who-honey-trapped-burger-king-victim-spotted-at-rai