20have%20rocked%20the%20Indian%20academic%20and%20political%20world%20with%20paper%20leaks%20being%20investigated%20by%20authorities%20at%20both%20central%20and%20state%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20was%20handed%20over%20the%20probe%20into%20NEET%20paper%20leaks%20last%20night%20as%20the%20government%20vowed%20to%20protect%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20students.%20It%20is%20also%20probing%20the%20UGC-NET%20irregularities%2C%20which%20include%20papers%20being%20leaked%20and%20sold%20on%20the%20dark%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20Police%20had%20earlier%20arrested%20four%20persons%20who%20had%20confessed%20to%20having%20leaked%20the%20question%20papers%20a%20night%20before%20the%20NEET%20UG%20exam.%C2%A0Cops%20are%20now%20probing%20the%20role%20of%20'solver%20gangs'%20that%20sell%20leaked%20exam%20papers%20to%20students%20and%20provide%20proxy%20candidates%20to%20take%20tests%20for%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20part%2C%20the%20government%20yesterday%20replaced%20the%20testing%20body%20head%20and%20formed%20a%20high-level%20panel%20to%20look%20into%20the%20NEET%20irregularities.%20A%20new%20law%20has%20also%20been%20notified%20to%20curb%20paper%20leaks%20and%20other%20exam%20malpractices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20taken%20the%20NEET%20UG%20test%20on%20May%205%2C%20but%20after%20the%20results%20were%20declared%20on%20June%204%2C%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leaks%20and%20grace%20marks%20given%20to%20over%201%2C500%20students%20surfaced.%20This%20triggered%20protests%20and%20court%20cases%2C%20and%20ultimately%20a%20CBI%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20afternoon%2C%20over%201%2C500%20aspirants%20will%20take%20a%20NEET%20re-test%20at%20seven%20exam%20centres%20after%20the%20testing%20agency%20withdrew%20the%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%20them%20to%20make%20up%20for%20loss%20of%20time.%20Officials%20of%20the%20exam%20body%20will%20be%20present%20to%20ensure%20the%20exams%20are%20held%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENEET%20PG%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20today%2C%20was%20cancelled%20last%20night%20with%20the%20Health%20ministry%20stating%20a%20new%20date%20will%20be%20announced%20soon.%20UGC-NET%20was%20also%20cancelled%20-%20just%20a%20day%20after%20it%20was%20already%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719123900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ft095ofhg_teachers-detained-in-maharashtra_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-teachers-detained-in-maharashtras-latur-5950108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20may%20not%20be%20the%20only%20state%20where%20malpractices%20were%20found%20during%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET%20with%20cops%20in%20Maharashtra%20questioning%20two%20teachers%20in%20the%20paper%20leak%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-teachers-detained-in-maharashtras-latur-5950108%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-teachers-detained-in-maharashtras-latur-5950108%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-teachers-detained-in-maharashtras-latur-5950108%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There's%20A%2072%25%20Chance%20That%20An%20Asteroid%20May%20Hit%20Earth%20On%20This%20Exact%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUS%20space%20agency%20NASA%2C%20in%20a%20hypothetical%20exercise%2C%20has%20found%20that%20a%20potentially%20hazardous%20asteroid%20has%20a%2072%25%20chance%20of%20hitting%20the%20Earth%20and%20we%20may%20not%20be%20adequately%20prepared%20to%20prevent%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fnews-release%2Fnasa-partners-conduct-fifth-asteroid-impact-exercise-release-summary%2F%5C%22%3Eofficial%20report%20by%20the%20space%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NASA%20conducted%20the%20fifth%20biennial%20Planetary%20Defense%20Interagency%20Tabletop%20Exercise%20in%20April.%20On%20June%2020%2C%20NASA%20unveiled%20the%20summary%20of%20the%20exercise%2C%20held%20at%20the%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Applied%20Physics%20Laboratory%20(APL)%20in%20Laurel%2C%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20tabletop%20exercise%2C%20apart%20from%20NASA%2C%20included%20nearly%20100%20representatives%20from%20various%20US%20government%20agencies%20and%20international%20collaborators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20there%20are%20no%20known%20significant%20asteroid%20threats%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20this%20was%20done%20to%20assess%20the%20Earth's%20ability%20to%20respond%20effectively%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20potentially%20hazardous%20asteroid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENASA%20stated%20that%20the%20hypothetical%20exercise%20also%20provided%20valuable%20insights%20about%20the%20risks%2C%20response%20options%2C%20and%20opportunities%20for%20collaboration%20posed%20by%20varying%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20planetary%20defence%20officer%20emeritus%20at%20NASA%20Headquarters%20in%20Washington%2C%20Lindley%20Johnson%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20uncertainties%20in%20these%20initial%20conditions%20for%20the%20exercise%20allowed%20participants%20to%20consider%20a%20particularly%20challenging%20set%20of%20circumstances.%20A%20large%20asteroid%20impact%20is%20potentially%20the%20only%20natural%20disaster%20humanity%20has%20the%20technology%20to%20predict%20years%20in%20advance%20and%20take%20action%20to%20prevent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Tabletop%20exercise%20summary%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20exercise%2C%20participants%20considered%20potential%20national%20and%20global%20responses%20to%20a%20hypothetical%20scenario%20in%20which%20a%20never-before-detected%20asteroid%20was%20identified%20that%20had%2C%20according%20to%20initial%20calculations%2C%20a%2072%25%20chance%20of%20hitting%20Earth%20in%20approximately%2014%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETo%20be%20precise%2C%20%E2%80%9C72%25%20chance%20of%20Earth%20impact%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fttx5-quicklook-report-final.pdf%3Femrc%3D66748d3b531ab%5C%22%3E12%20July%202038%3C%2Fa%3E%20(14.25%20years%20warning%20time).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20this%20preliminary%20observation%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20precisely%20determine%20the%20asteroid's%20size%2C%20composition%2C%20and%20long-term%20trajectory%2C%20added%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Earth's%20key%20gaps%2C%20the%20summary%20highlighted%2C%20%E2%80%9CDecision-making%20processes%20and%20risk%20tolerance%20not%20understood.%20Limited%20readiness%20to%20quickly%20implement%20needed%20space%20missions.%20Timely%20global%20coordination%20of%20messaging%20needs%20attention.%20Asteroid-impact%20disaster%20management%20plans%20are%20not%20defined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20exercise%20to%20use%20data%20from%20NASA's%20DART%20(Double%20Asteroid%20Redirection%20Test)%20mission.%20DART%20is%20the%20first%20in-space%20demonstration%20of%20a%20technology%20for%20defending%20the%20planet%20against%20potential%20asteroid%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDART%20has%20also%20confirmed%20that%20a%20kinetic%20impactor%20could%20change%20the%20trajectory%20of%20an%20asteroid%2C%20stated%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20informed%20that%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Earth%20will%20have%20time%20to%20evaluate%20and%20respond%20to%20a%20potentially%20hazardous%20asteroid%2C%20NASA%20is%20developing%20NEO%20Surveyor%20(Near-Earth%20Object%20Surveyor).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENEO%20Surveyor%20is%20an%20infrared%20space%20telescope.%20It%20is%20designed%20specifically%20to%20expedite%20humanity's%20ability%20to%20discover%20most%20of%20the%20potentially%20hazardous%20near-Earth%20objects%20many%20years%20before%20they%20could%20become%20an%20impact%20threat.%20NASA's%20NEO%20Surveyor%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20June%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719122760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3jjudlqg_asteroid_625x300_13_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-exercise-finds-asteroid-with-72-chance-of-hitting-earth-5950284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20space%20agency%20NASA%2C%20in%20a%20hypothetical%20exercise%2C%20has%20found%20that%20a%20potentially%20hazardous%20asteroid%20has%20a%2072%25%20chance%20of%20hitting%20the%20Earth%20and%20we%20may%20not%20be%20adequately%20prepared%20to%20prevent%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-exercise-finds-asteroid-with-72-chance-of-hitting-earth-5950284%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-exercise-finds-asteroid-with-72-chance-of-hitting-earth-5950284%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-exercise-finds-asteroid-with-72-chance-of-hitting-earth-5950284%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20MLA's%20Nephew%20Arrested%20After%20SUV%20Hits%20Bike%20On%20National%20Highway%2C%201%20Dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2019-year-old%20man%20has%20died%20after%20a%20car%20driven%20by%20the%20nephew%20of%20a%20Maharashtra%20MLA%20hit%20a%20bike%20on%20Pune-Nashik%20national%20highway%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20arrested%20Mayur%20Mohite%3B%20he%20is%20the%20nephew%20of%20Dilip%20Mohite%20Patil%2C%20MLA%20from%20Pune%20district's%20Khed%20Alandi%20Assembly%20segment.%20Dilip%20Mohite%20Patil%20belongs%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Om%20Bhalerao.%20A%20police%20officer%20has%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20the%20Toyota%20Fortuner%20SUV%20driven%20by%20Mayur%20Mohite%20was%20coming%20from%20the%20wrong%20side%20and%20hit%20the%20bike%20head%20on.%20Further%20probe%2C%20police%20said%2C%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20media%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20legislator%20has%20said%20that%20his%20nephew%20did%20not%20flee%20the%20spot.%20He%20has%20also%20stressed%20that%20he%20was%20not%20intoxicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20yet%20again%20put%20rash%20driving%20in%20Pune%20under%20the%20spotlight.%20Last%20month%2C%20two%2024-year-old%20software%20engineers%20died%20after%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%2C%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20the%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20realtor%2C%20hit%20their%20bike%20from%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20accused%2C%20who%20was%20driving%20drunk%2C%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20accident%20on%20terms%20widely%20seen%20as%20lenient.%20This%20sparked%20national%20outrage%20and%20prompted%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20to%20modify%20its%20order%20and%20sent%20the%20accused%20to%20an%20observation%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20since%20found%20evidence%20of%20how%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20teen%20attempted%20a%20cover-up%20and%20several%20of%20them%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719122160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvg5hd79o_pune-accident-mla-nephew_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdilip-mohite-p