Super%208%20Group%20a%20big%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20stand%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20India%20are%20top%20of%20the%20Super%208%20Group%201%20with%20two%20wins%20in%20two%20matches.%20Australia%20and%20Afghanistan%20have%20won%20one%20game%20apiece%20from%20their%20two%20matches%20while%20Bangladesh%20have%20lost%20both%20of%20their%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Afghanistan's%20win%20against%20Australia%20means%20for%20India%20and%20the%20Super%208%20Group%201%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAustralia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(NRR%20of%20%2B0.223)%2C%20who%20are%20next%20to%20face%20India%20in%20the%20Super%208s%2C%20now%20have%20a%20must-win%20clash%20ahead%20of%20them%20as%20a%20defeat%20against%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20men%20could%20be%20curtains%20for%20them%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20If%20Australia%20suffer%20a%20defeat%20against%20India%20and%20Afghanistan%20beat%20Bangladesh%20in%20their%20next%20match%2C%20the%20Afghans%20will%20be%20through%20to%20the%20semi-finals%20alongside%20India%2C%20and%20Australia%20will%20be%20knocked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20%3Cstrong%3EIndia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20victory%20against%20Australia%20would%20confirm%20their%20progression%20but%20a%20defeat%20can%20make%20things%20a%20little%20tricky%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20margin%20of%20loss%20is%20a%20big%20one.%20India's%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20of%20%2B2.425%20is%20an%20incredibly%20strong%20one.%20But%2C%20in%20cricket%2C%20you%20never%20say%20never.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fqrdke2bo_super-8_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3D