2%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-another-secret-child-with-neuralink-employee-report-5950152%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-another-secret-child-with-neuralink-employee-report-5950152%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-another-secret-child-with-neuralink-employee-report-5950152%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO's%20Hat-Trick%20In%20Pushpak%20Safe%20Landing%2C%20Focus%20Now%20On%20Orbital%20Entry%20Trials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20distinction%20for%20any%20space%20agency%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20today%20achieved%20a%20rare%20hat-trick%20of%20the%20safe%20landing%20of%20an%20uncrewed%2C%20autonomous%20winged%20reusable%20launch%20vehicle%20during%20an%20experiment%20in%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20has%20proudly%20achieved%20a%20third%20consecutive%20success%20in%20the%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20Landing%20Experiment%20(LEX)%20today.%20%26quot%3BThe%20third%20and%20final%20test%20in%20the%20series%20of%20LEX%20(03)%20was%20conducted%20at%2007%3A10%20IST%20at%20the%20Aeronautical%20Test%20Range%20(ATR)%20in%20Chitradurga%2C%20Karnataka%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHat-trick%20for%20ISRO%20in%20RLV%20LEX!%20%F0%9F%9A%80%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3ISRO%20achieved%20its%20third%20and%20final%20consecutive%20success%20in%20the%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20Landing%20EXperiment%20(LEX)%20on%20June%2023%2C%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BPushpak%26quot%3B%20executed%20a%20precise%20horizontal%20landing%2C%20showcasing%20advanced%20autonomous%20capabilities%20under%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcGMrw6mmyH%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcGMrw6mmyH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1804695916617863425%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20chairman%20S%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BISRO%20achieved%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20safe%20landings%20by%20the%20Pushpak%20or%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%2C%20now%20this%20sets%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20orbital%20test%20of%20Pushpak.%20It%20will%20be%20launched%20on%20a%20rocket%20into%20space%2C%20and%20then%20it%20can%20safely%20land%20on%20Earth.%20Truly%20a%20game-changer%20technology%20to%20reduce%20cost%20of%20access%20to%20space.%20A%20uniquely%20atmanirbhar%20effort%20by%20ISRO%20to%20harness%20reusable%20rockets%20in%20a%20swadeshi%20way%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBringing%20the%20most%20expensive%20part%20of%20the%20rocket%20that%20houses%20the%20electronics%20is%20what%20makes%20Pushpak%20the%20futuristic%20rocket%20tech%20for%20India.%20ISRO%20continues%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20master%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20big%20test%20will%20come%20when%20India%20goes%20in%20for%20the%20orbital%20test.%20Mr%20Somanath%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Orbital%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(ORV)%20will%20have%20high%20temperature%20protection%20tiles%20on%20its%20outer%20surface.%20Liquid%20rocket%20engines%20and%20a%20retractable%20landing%20gear.%20It%20will%20also%20have%20space%20for%20a%20payload%20that%20can%20be%20deployed%20through%20a%20door%20that%20will%20open.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20India's%20own%20delta%20winged%20'space%20shuttle'%20of%20sorts%2C%20though%20uncrewed%2C%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20big%20leap%20of%20faith%20at%20a%20point%20where%20other%20agencies%20are%20only%20attempting%20to%20bring%20back%20spent%20hollow%20rocket%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20whole%20new%20vehicle%20much%20larger%20in%20size%20will%20be%20made%20for%20the%20orbital%20test%20based%20on%20the%20success%20of%20today's%20test%20and%20it%20will%20first%20be%20tested%20in%20a%20landing%20experiment%20before%20it%20is%20flown%20into%20space%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20Earth%20like%20a%20space%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20says%20following%20the%20success%20of%20the%20RLV%20(Reusable%20Landing%20Vehicle)%20LEX-01%20and%20LEX-02%20missions%2C%20RLV%20LEX-03%20re-demonstrated%20the%20autonomous%20landing%20capability%20of%20the%20RLV%20under%20more%20challenging%20release%20conditions%20(cross%20range%20of%20500%20m%20against%20150%20m%20for%20LEX-02)%20and%20more%20severe%20wind%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22lv%5C%22%3ERLV-LEX3%20Video%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMkYLP4asYY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMkYLP4asYY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1804709607576834363%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20winged%20vehicle%2C%20'Pushpak'%2C%20was%20released%20from%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20Chinook%20Helicopter%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%204.5%20km.%20From%20a%20release%20point%204.5%20km%20away%20from%20the%20runway%2C%20Pushpak%20autonomously%20executed%20cross-range%20correction%20manoeuvres%2C%20approached%20the%20runway%20and%20performed%20a%20precise%20horizontal%20landing%20at%20the%20runway%20centreline.%20Due%20to%20this%20vehicle's%20low%20lift-to-drag%20ratio%20aerodynamic%20configuration%2C%20the%20landing%20velocity%20exceeded%20320%20kmph%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20260%20kmph%20for%20a%20commercial%20aircraft%20and%20280%20kmph%20for%20a%20typical%20fighter%20aircraft.%20After%20touchdown%2C%20the%20vehicle%20velocity%20was%20reduced%20to%20nearly%20100%20kmph%20using%20its%20brake%20parachute%2C%20after%20which%20the%20landing%20gear%20brakes%20were%20employed%20for%20deceleration%20and%20stop%20on%20the%20runway.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20this%20ground%20roll%20phase%2C%20Pushpak%20utilises%20its%20rudder%20and%20nose%20wheel%20steering%20system%20to%20autonomously%20maintain%20a%20stable%20and%20precise%20ground%20roll%20along%20the%20runway%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ISRO%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%2C%20this%20mission%20simulated%20the%20approach%20and%20landing%20interface%20and%20high-speed%20landing%20conditions%20for%20a%20vehicle%20returning%20from%20space%2C%20reaffirming%20ISRO's%20expertise%20in%20acquiring%20the%20most%20critical%20technologies%20required%20for%20the%20development%20of%20a%20RLV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20mission%2C%20the%20advanced%20guidance%20algorithm%20catering%20to%20longitudinal%20and%20lateral%20plane%20error%20corrections%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20the%20future%20Orbital%20Re-entry%20Mission%2C%20has%20been%20validated.%20The%20RLV-LEX%20uses%20multi-sensor%20fusion%20including%20sensors%20like%20inertial%20sensor%2C%20Radar%20altimeter%2C%20Flush%20air%20data%20system%2C%20Pseudolite%20system%20and%20NavIC.%20Notably%2C%20the%20RLV-LEX-03%20mission%20reused%20the%20winged%20body%20and%20flight%20systems%20as%20such%20without%20any%20modification%2C%20from%20the%20LEX-02%20mission%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20robustness%20of%20ISRO's%20capability%20of%20design%20to%20reuse%20flight%20systems%20for%20multiple%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mission%20simulates%20the%20approach%20and%20landing%20interface%20and%20high-speed%20landing%20conditions%20for%20a%20vehicle%20returning%20from%20space%2C%20which%20will%20reaffirm%20ISRO's%20expertise%20in%20acquiring%20the%20most%20critical%20technologies%20required%20for%20the%20development%20of%20a%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20asserts%20ISRO%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20embarked%20on%20making%20its%20own%20version%20of%20the%20swadeshi%20'space%20shuttle'%20by%20planning%20about%20it%20more%20than%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20actual%20work%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20started%2010%20years%20ago%20when%20a%20dedicated%20team%20of%20engineers%20and%20scientists%20plunged%20into%20making%20RLV%20a%20reality.%20The%206.5%20metre%20aeroplane-like%20spacecraft%20weighs%201.75%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20descent%20phase%2C%20which%20is%20essentially%20a%20glider%20like%20event%2C%20small%20thrusters%20will%20help%20the%20vehicle%20to%20be%20navigated%20to%20the%20exact%20spot%20where%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20shuttle%20or%20RLV%20has%20taken%20more%20than%2010%20years%20and%20the%20government%20has%20invested%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somanath%20congratulated%20the%20team%20for%20their%20efforts%20in%20maintaining%20the%20success%20streak%20in%20such%20complex%20missions.%20Dr%20S%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20director%20of%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Centre%2C%20emphasised%20that%20this%20consistent%20success%20boosts%20ISRO's%20confidence%20in%20the%20critical%20technologies%20essential%20for%20future%20orbital%20re-entry%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719117060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fipnvdia8_isro-pushpak_625x300_23_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe-landing-focus-now-on-orbital-entry-trials-5950142%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20rare%20distinction%20for%20any%20space%20agency%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20today%20achieved%20a%20rare%20hat-trick%20of%20safe%20landing%20of%20an%20uncrewed%2C%20autonomous%20winged%20reusable%20launch%20vehicle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe-landing-focus-now-on-orbital-entry-trials-5950142%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe-landing-focus-now-on-orbital-entry-trials-5950142%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe-landing-focus-now-on-orbital-entry-trials-5950142%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWanted%20To%20Come%20Back%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Hardik's%20Emotional%20Remark%2C%20Namedrops%20Dravid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya's%20downward%20spiral%20started%20last%20year%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20a%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20game%20but%20the%20star%20all-rounder%20always%20believed%20that%20fortune%20favours%20the%20brave%20if%20they%20hang%20around.%20First%20it%20was%20back-to-back%20injuries%20that%20kept%20him%20out%20for%20four%20months%20and%20then%20a%20very%20rocky%20two%20months%20in%20the%20IPL%20as%20MI%20skipper%2C%20there%20was%20no%20silver%20lining%20for%20India's%20best%20all-rounder%20in%20contemporary%20times%20until%20this%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20regained%20his%20mojo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20fortunate%20to%20play%20for%20the%20country%2C%20it%20was%20a%20freak%20injury%20I%20had%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20come%20back%20but%20God%20had%20other%20plans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20said%20after%20scoring%20a%2027-ball-50%20and%20taking%20a%20wicket%20in%20India's%2050-run%20victory%20over%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20it%20was%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20different%20World%20Cup%20format%2C%20Pandya%20walked%20away%20with%20an%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20speaking%20to%20our%20coach%20Rahul%20sir%20(Dravid)%20and%20he%20said%20'Luck%20comes%20to%20people%20who%20work%20hard'%20and%20that%20has%20stuck%20with%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20award%20this%20day%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20played%20really%20good%20cricket.%20More%20than%20anything%20we%20have%20stuck%20together%20and%20executed%20our%20plans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Pandya's%20half-century%20and%20contributions%20from%20Virat%20Kohli%20(37)%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(36)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(34)%20took%20India%20to%20196%20for%205%20after%20being%20put%20into%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20predicted%20at%20the%20break%20that%20it%20would%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWicket%20looked%20alright%2C%20par%20would've%20been%20180%2C%20we%20got%20196.%20That's%20a%20good%20score%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20told%20broadcasters%20at%20the%20innings%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20Dube%2C%20who%20has%20so%20far%20struggled%2C%20for%20playing%20a%20composed%20innings%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20point%20Shivam%20went%20(in)%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20wickets%20were%20lost.%20He%20had%20to%20take%20his%20time%20and%20we%20did%20well%20to%20recover.%20His%20strength%20is%20to%20take%20down%20spinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20time%20came%2C%20when%20we%20could%20go%20hard%2C%20we%20went%20(after%20their%20bowling)%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20star%20all-rounder%20believed%20that%20the%20pitch%20would%20get%20slower%20as%20the%20match%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20it%20tends%20to%20get%20slower%20in%20the%20end%2C%20some%20balls%20were%20sliding%20down%20when%20bowled%20at%20the%20right%20length%2C%20discipline%20and%20good%20bowling%20should%20do%20the%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20cross%20wind%20blowing%20across%20Sir%20Vivian%20Richards%20Stadium%20and%20Pandya%20spoke%20about%20using%20the%20breeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20realise%20the%20batters%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20breeze%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20I%20did%20not%20give%20them%20a%20chance%20where%20the%20wind%20was%20blowing%2C%20it%20was%20about%20being%20one%20step%20ahead%20as%20a%20batter.%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20did%20agree%20that%20there%20is%20room%20for%20improvement%20as%20a%20batting%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20as%20a%20group%20can%20get%20better%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20places%2C%20losing%20wickets%20in%20bunches%20is%20something%20we%20can%20rectify%20and%20get%20better%20at%2C%20apart%20from%20that%2C%20we%20are%20looking%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAshwin's%20take%20on%20individual%20scores%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20senior%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20astute%20analysts%20among%20active%20international%20cricketers%2C%20said%20time%20has%20come%20for%20fans%20to%20look%20at%20the%20impactful%2020s%20and%2030s%20as%20good%20contributions%20rather%20than%20milestone%20half-centuries%20or%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20used%20to%20an%20approach%20where%20batsmen%20throw%20it%20away%20after%20making%2030's%2020's%2C%20but%20it%20is%20about%20time%20we%20embrace%20an%20approach%20like%20this%20especially%20while%20batting%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTop%20Intent%20from%20all%20the%20Indian%20batters%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwin%20wrote%20on%20X%20about%20India%20reaching%20nearly%20200%20with%20just%20a%20single%20half-century%20and%20three%20contributions%20upwards%20of%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719114780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F3infotn8_hardik-pandya_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%