s%2C%20subsequent%20investigations%20by%20Bihar%20Police%20uncovered%20a%20different%20aspect%3A%20the%20exam%20paper%20had%20been%20leaked%20to%20select%20candidates%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20NTA's%20attempts%20to%20manage%20the%20fallout%2C%20accusations%20of%20a%20widespread%20leak%20persisted%2C%20prompting%20protests%20and%20legal%20cases%20nationwide.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20intervened%2C%20chastising%20the%20NTA%20for%20handling%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Solver%20Gang%20And%20Its%20Network%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20the%20paper%20leak%20is%20Atri's%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20syndicate%20known%20as%20the%20'solver%20gang'.%20This%20network%20specialized%20in%20obtaining%20and%20distributing%20solved%20question%20papers%20via%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20catering%20to%20aspirants%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20hefty%20price%20for%20guaranteed%20success.%20Atri%2C%20already%20infamous%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20previous%20exam%20paper%20leaks%2C%20operated%20with%20impunity%20across%20various%20states%2C%20leveraging%20his%20connections%20within%20the%20'exam%20mafia'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtri's%20modus%20operandi%20involved%20obtaining%20the%20exam%20papers%20well%20in%20advance%2C%20typically%20a%20day%20before%20the%20examination%2C%20and%20swiftly%20disseminating%20them%20to%20paying%20clients%20through%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gang%20also%20offered%20students%20the%20option%20of%20paying%20more%20and%20getting%20a%20'Munna%20Bhai'%2C%20a%20proxy%20who%20would%20give%20the%20exam%20in%20their%20place.%20The%20candidates%20were%20assured%20that%20the%20'Munna%20Bhai'%20would%20score%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERavi%20Atri%3A%20Medical%20Aspirant%20To%20Exam%20Mafia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20Ravi%20Atri's%20parents%20sent%20him%20to%20Rajasthan's%20Kota%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam.%20After%20years%20of%20preparation%2C%20he%20cleared%20the%20exam%20in%202012%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20PGI%20Rohtak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20dropped%20out%20in%20the%20fourth%20year%2C%20and%20authorities%20say%20that%20by%20then%20he%20had%20come%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20'exam%20mafia'%20and%20was%20sitting%20as%20a%20proxy%20for%20other%20candidates.%20He%20also%20started%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20circulating%20the%20leaked%20papers%20among%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanjeev%20Mukhiya%2C%20Another%20Key%20Figure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjeev%20Mukhiya%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20'solver%20gang'%2C%20has%20been%20identified%20by%20police%20as%20a%20central%20figure%20in%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak.%20Police%20are%20conducting%20raids%20at%20possible%20locations%20linked%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhiya%20does%20not%20stand%20alone%20in%20his%20family's%20criminal%20background.%20Sources%20reveal%20his%20son's%20arrest%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20leaked%20question%20papers%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20teacher%20recruitment%20exams%20conducted%20by%20BPSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20a%20network%20extending%20from%20constable%20recruitment%20exams%20to%20teacher%20recruitment%20exams%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20illustrating%20the%20scale%20and%20reach%20of%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20that%20Mukhiya%20may%20have%20fled%20to%20Nepal%20after%20the%20controversy%20snowballed%2C%20complicating%20extradition%20procedures%20due%20to%20the%20bilateral%20agreements%20between%20India%20and%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20ruled%20out%20cancellation%20of%20NEET%2C%20saying%20he%20cannot%20jeopardise%20careers%20of%20lakhs%20of%20students%20who%20cleared%20the%20exam%20rightfully%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bisolated%20incidents%20of%20malpractices%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20government%20has%20also%20initiated%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20case%2C%20and%20operationalised%20a%20stringent%20law%20that%20aims%20to%20curb%20malpractices%20and%20irregularities%20in%20competitive%20examinations.%20A%20maximum%20jail%20term%20of%2010%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20offenders%20are%20some%20of%20the%20tough%20measures%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719112860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F71sc5k0s_ravi-atri-neet-exam-leak_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'solver%20gang'%20that%20leaks%20exam%20papers%20and%20also%20provides%20proxy%20candidates%20who%20would%20sit%20for%20an%20exam%20has%20come%20into%20the%20limelight%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20the%20medical%20entrance%20test%20NEET.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BConsidering%20Everything...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit's%20Clear%20Post-Match%20Verdict%20On%20Hardik%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya's%20batting%20always%20puts%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20in%20a%20good%20stead%E2%80%9D%2C%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20reiterated%20the%20ability%20of%20his%20team's%20biggest%20%E2%80%98X-Factor'%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%20after%20his%20fifty%20against%20Bangladesh%20all%20but%20put%20'Men%20in%20Blue'%20into%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Pandya%2C%20who%20scored%20the%20first%20half-century%20by%20an%20Indian%20No.%206%20in%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%20game%2C%20also%20took%20a%20wicket%20in%20the%20team's%2050-run%20Super%208s%20win%20against%20Bangladesh%20here%20on%20Saturday.%20Pandya%20has%20so%20far%20scored%2089%20runs%20in%20three%20innings%20with%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20141%2C%20besides%20taking%20eight%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20mentioned%20in%20the%20last%20game%20as%20well%2C%20his%20batting%20well%20puts%20us%20in%20a%20good%20stead.%20We%20want%20to%20finish%20well%20and%20Hardik%20being%20Hardik%20we%20know%20what%20he%20is%20capable%20of%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20very%20important%20player%20for%20us%2C%20if%20he%20can%20keep%20doing%20that%2C%20it%20will%20put%20us%20in%20good%20positions%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%2C%20Indian%20batters%20also%20showed%20more%20intent%20and%20there%20were%20quickfire%2030s%20from%20three%20batters%20--%20Virat%20Kohli%20(37)%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(36)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(34).%20The%20skipper%20himself%20set%20the%20tone%20with%2023%20off%2011%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20talking%20about%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time%20now.%20It's%20about%20going%20there%20and%20putting%20that%20into%20work.%20Considering%20everything%20we%20played%20really%20well%2C%20adapted%20to%20the%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20eight%20batters%20need%20to%20play%20their%20role%2C%20whatever%20it%20is.%20We%20saw%20one%20guy%20get%2050%20and%20we%20got%20197%2C%20in%20T20%20I%20don't%20believe%20we%20need%20to%20get%20fifties%20and%20hundreds%2C%20what%20matters%20is%20the%20pressure%20you%20put%20on%20the%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20batters%20from%20the%20word%20go%20pl