cing%20yoga%20at%2050%20and%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20share%20its%20benefits%20with%20the%20world.%20The%20101-year-old%20was%20recently%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20her%20remarkable%20contribution%20to%20spreading%20awareness%20about%20yoga.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98This%20Exam%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20For%20You%E2%80%99%3A%20IAS%20Officer%20Dealt%20With%204%20Failures%20to%20Crack%20UPSC%20CSE%20With%20AIR%208%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20it%20taking%20so%20long%20for%20you%20to%20clear%20the%20exam%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20exam%20isn%E2%80%99t%20for%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaipur-resident%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Singhal%20was%20often%20questioned%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20appear%20for%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20exams%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352526%2Fupsc-cse-ias-officer-aditya-pandey-personality-test-interview-round-preparation-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnion%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20%3C%2Fa%3E(UPSC)%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20stepped%20out%2C%20people%20would%20question%20what%20was%20going%20on%20in%20my%20life%20and%20say%20that%20I%20was%20stuck.%20People%20said%20clearing%20UPSC%20was%20not%20my%20cup%20of%20tea%20and%20I%20should%20prepare%20for%20other%20exams%20like%20SSC%20%5BStaff%20Selection%20Commission%5D%2C%20RAS%20%5BRajasthan%20Administrative%20Services%5D%2C%20or%20SBI%20%5BState%20Bank%20of%20India%5D%20clerk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Ashish%20%E2%