ifferent%20things%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20course%20%E2%80%94%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20food%20design%20in%20Milan%2C%20which%20interested%20me%20deeply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20doing%20something%20in%20the%20food%20domain%20where%20he%20could%20use%20his%20creativity%20and%20artistry%20motivated%20Akash.%20After%20completing%20his%20degree%2C%20he%20spent%20a%20year%20travelling%20across%20Europe%2C%20engaging%20in%20various%20internships%20that%20helped%20him%20uncover%20his%20future%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20about%20how%20food%20is%20viewed%20outside%20India.%20I%20worked%20with%20a%20food%20designer%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20but%20what%20I%20missed%20there%20was%20a%20genuine%20connection%20with%20food.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20work%20with%20Italian%20or%20Dutch%20food.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20with%20South%20Indian%20food%20and%20bring%20out%20the%20elements%20of%20our%20cooking%20and%20showcase%20it%20to%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%20wanted%20to%20share%20the%20stories%20and%20history%20behind%20everyday%20food%20in%20a%20modern%20way.%20So%2C%20in%202021%2C%20he%20founded%20%E2%80%98Vizha%20Medai%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20design%20studio%20started%20with%20two%20of%20his%20architecture%20college%20mates.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20multidisciplinary%20studio%20specialising%20in%20event%20design%20and%20decor%2C%20menu%20curation%2C%20outfit%20design%20and%20styling%2C%20and%20creative%20direction.%20They%20curate%20%E2%80%9Cfood%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20art%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20common%20thread%20of%20local%20essence%2C%20says%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWeaving%20a%20story%20around%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20thread%20throughout%20Akash%E2%80%99s%20life%20has%20been%20his%20need%20to%20share%20food%20stories.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%20100-day%20cooking%20project%20to%20shed%20light%